{"tid":984544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法巴交易主管聖誕勁輸8,000萬美元 之後不返工","createTime":"2019-01-17T01:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T03:56:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61086c03d644a073449f61ed2484ecc326c2963f","tid":984544,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:42:24.000Z","msg":"去年12月美股出乎意料地大跌，一眾大行交易員大跌眼鏡，有一名法國巴黎銀行的交易主管，於聖誕假期放假前下重注交易標普500指數衍生工具，虧損了8,000萬美元，這名主管長假期後至昨日並沒有上班。<br />\n<br />\n根據《彭博》引述知情人士透露，該行的美國指數交易主管Antoine Lours因為看好標普500的走勢，所以在放聖誕節假前決定投資相關的衍生工具。在聖誕節假期之後幾日，由於市場憂慮中美貿易戰升溫，美股經過多次暴跌，所以Antoine Lours的投資損失慘重，但Lours在聖誕假後一直沒有上班。<br />\n<br />\nLours沒有回應在LinkedIn針對他的評論，而他一位在紐約的同事指，Lours本周亦沒有上班。法巴駐紐約的發言人Ilias Catsaros則拒絕發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n巨額損失增加了法巴交易部門的負擔。而法國另一間較小型的投行Natixis SA的報告指出，他們在12月亞洲股票衍生品交易中虧損了2.6億歐元（2.96億美元）。<br />\n<br />\ninvestMAN<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190116/59150617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59150617&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=38c021f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59150617&h=ddb81d85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190116/59150617</a>"},{"pid":"f67f3c0f45684151a53e1d3b395610b7020e9345","tid":984544,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:43:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26996a27dff6d086edcb40b9e1be406ba3e3fcb7","tid":984544,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:02:16.000Z","msg":"被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be853991812e59e51fb1a1e453ee61f1f063eeb","tid":984544,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:05:07.000Z","msg":"呢d 工真係好爽, 用公司錢豪賭, 輸左無事, 贏左